Trinity::

She looked up at them, worry showing on her face. "Will Aerotaur be 
ok? He's not going to join the matrix is he?"  She started to 
cry. "He can't go be with Mom and Dad.  He can't. It's not fair, I 
lost Mom and Dad, I can't lose Uncle Aerotaur too. It's not fair!" 
she shouted and took off running down the hallway, crying.
